{"tid":454971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[打工仔]有冇人好憎公司總有個工作狂？","createTime":"2017-11-01T15:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T06:58:46.000Z","uid":22244,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d025c21ab20bfe32714e450ecd7fbeb0b8f86c","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"新入一間公司，本身個工作狂對我都幾好態度唔錯<br />\n但之後我發現佢工作狂到爆，返9點30<br />\n佢8點幾已經係公司做野，跟住一定盡量令自己好撚多野做<br />\n乜都攬黎做，咁依樣都冇問題<br />\n最幣係佢成撚日黑面發脾氣，屌你忙關我撚事咩<br />\n搞到我新入黎唔敢問佢野，成日都要靠自己估估下<br />\n我問其他人又唔得，話我應該問佢野，意思話我唔尊重佢<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，依家對我既態度差左好多，<br />\n我又冇得罪佢好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e8e5c37cb1f4bdf11fe4c5d626e8ab9e3063df","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a28381615d7e1dbed9ad2d92c5dccfb91d5be48","tid":454971,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"你唔識直接同佢反映?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9b7d7b1fd659502d7f696d3bafeedbe406b120","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔識直接同佢反映?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢點反映？我係under佢架<br />\n唔通同佢講你態度可唔可以好返d"},{"pid":"a477c51e10c5f58186bb52e54c37642f6a6b125e","tid":454971,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11cfaab416d4462fee11f17040f2f9d74f24c6d5","tid":454971,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:10:52.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪有嘢唔識又唔問 做錯又要佢執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefe3a894b10fc061768532da763b104399b823b","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d傻佬來 係咁勁佢自己做左老闆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都咁話，仲自稱自己唔做野唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63abe4130c187fb92ff4e48d54ec081b5a8fcd3","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪有嘢唔識又唔問 做錯又要佢執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，當我問佢就好燥底咁求其好快咁講，<br />\n仲要恥笑方式咁"},{"pid":"fb107f2ca3d2c6ce7a82c503985fd604b40af7e4","tid":454971,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:31:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c9aeab76e98b811460667cd7b0ce8d9881c0bd","tid":454971,"uid":68165,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"扮工狂衰d<br />\n日日遲走大大聲呻多野做<br />\n但其實自己1999做野慢同垃圾"},{"pid":"5edd611ee536381af2c351e2ba60a136da65c3a5","tid":454971,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:33:45.000Z","msg":"樓主都on9 <br />\n黑面咪由柒佢   <br />\n翻工預咗受氣<br />\n阿頭發你脾氣<br />\n份人工包咗ga"},{"pid":"29d60ca74e80f10df4595d16416ff5667659a9c1","tid":454971,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪有嘢唔識又唔問 做錯又要佢執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，當我問佢就好燥底咁求其好快咁講，<br />\n仲要恥笑方式咁</blockquote><br />\n你新入職佢教你係應份。對呢d老屎忽儘量早d學識之後就各走各路。"},{"pid":"34a1c8b9a8a210c2fb0431146fed75fed1956373","tid":454971,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔明同工作狂有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係憎佢脾氣差同小氣唔教你野姐<br />\n有脾氣好嘅工作狂<br />\n亦有又懶又小氣又脾氣差嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303d715901b8bcee246ae623c9aea1c7d8366116","tid":454971,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d傻佬來 係咁勁佢自己做左老闆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都咁話，仲自稱自己唔做野唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呢d人你要小心啦。佢地通常都好介意教新人。因為佢地驚教識哂你就冇位企。你唔識成日問佢就一定踩住上背後就話9你教完你又唔識。呢d正仆街黎。"},{"pid":"187d52d9571ac7c306d19895d75c9362a24f3c1e","tid":454971,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c787c04485cd5609057442430220f3b5394d132","tid":454971,"uid":70928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港好多人鐘意做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慣左</blockquote><br />\n係咪同個盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b74dfaa70fc304cf78f7d9e986fe088bf33b19","tid":454971,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主都on9 <br />\n黑面咪由柒佢   <br />\n翻工預咗受氣<br />\n阿頭發你脾氣<br />\n份人工包咗ga</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35f1af6167ef95caf3e852c746868e92702e88f","tid":454971,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港好多人鐘意做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慣左</blockquote><br />\n上面有一隻"},{"pid":"381df2ff1c8f6f9ecc4ef2a2ba0454c0a4fd4305","tid":454971,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T00:59:25.000Z","msg":"點解可以返工返到以為間公司係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ad8f12b8d411031febfe87bbaadd92a32f8ed9","tid":454971,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以返工返到以為間公司係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d人既人生多數無其他興趣/目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好可以24小時比佢地返工"},{"pid":"465fa8a53e44357a704d8e7f88e3d634703bdb01","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主都on9 <br />\n黑面咪由柒佢   <br />\n翻工預咗受氣<br />\n阿頭發你脾氣<br />\n份人工包咗ga</blockquote><br />\n你不如比埋條命公司好冇？"},{"pid":"ec675d9ba7daa99c554d5d72a1b993db0fa326f6","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係咪有嘢唔識又唔問 做錯又要佢執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，當我問佢就好燥底咁求其好快咁講，<br />\n仲要恥笑方式咁</blockquote><br />\n你新入職佢教你係應份。對呢d老屎忽儘量早d學識之後就各走各路。</blockquote><br />\n其實之前返工放工撞到佢同車都會傾下計笑下<br />\n依家儘量扮睇唔到佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e9a079f6b22492b7c6fa889df529fa91004b37","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完都唔明同工作狂有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係憎佢脾氣差同小氣唔教你野姐<br />\n有脾氣好嘅工作狂<br />\n亦有又懶又小氣又脾氣差嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前間公司有脾氣好既工作狂<br />\n我好like佢，因為佢肯教野，問佢野好有心教你<br />\n而唔係一副問問問乜都問既樣，到你問其他人又屌你"},{"pid":"e31b6dc07fbeb4f091cfb368a6188b22106ce891","tid":454971,"uid":22244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢d傻佬來 係咁勁佢自己做左老闆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都咁話，仲自稱自己唔做野唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呢d人你要小心啦。佢地通常都好介意教新人。因為佢地驚教識哂你就冇位企。你唔識成日問佢就一定踩住上背後就話9你教完你又唔識。呢d正仆街黎。</blockquote><br />\n有冇咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果個男人黎應該唔會咁掛"}]}